+- ‚úÖ **Create Events** - Authentication prompt with redirect to login
+- ‚úÖ **Manage Events** - Edit, delete, and host controls
+- ‚úÖ **Personal Dashboard** - View user's own events  
+- ‚úÖ **User Profile** - Account settings and preferences
+- ‚úÖ **RSVP Management** - Guest responses and invitations
+
