+}
+```
+
+### **2. Navigation Structure** 
+```
+App Layout (No Auth Gate)
+‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ (tabs) - Always accessible
+‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ index (Home) - Public + Personal events
+‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ events - Public events listing
+‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ services - Public marketplace
+‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ explore - Public markdown content
+‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ (auth) - Login/Signup flows
+‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ events/create - Protected route
+‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ events/[id] - Public event details
+```
+
+### **3. EventService Enhancements**
+```typescript
+// New public methods
+static async getPublicEvents(limit): Promise<Event[]>
